LOCUS       VKRSLUC1                4952 bp    DNA     circular SYN 03-APR-2026
DEFINITION  Illustrative VKORC1 rs9923231 upstream fragment to luciferase
            reporter construct for GENtle hero figure export.
ACCESSION   VKRSLUC1
VERSION     VKRSLUC1.1
KEYWORDS    synthetic construct; luciferase reporter; VKORC1; rs9923231.
SOURCE      synthetic construct
  ORGANISM  synthetic construct
            artificial sequences; vectors.
COMMENT     Synthetic documentation asset used to obtain a real circular DNA
            sequence-window SVG export for the VKORC1/rs9923231 luciferase
            hero figure. Sequence content is illustrative; feature geometry is
            curated for communication rather than wet-lab execution.
